{
  "video_id": "NDQ1Mi5I4rg",
  "title": "The gift and power of emotional courage | Susan David",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13167.0,
      "end_time": 14357.0,
      "text": "Hello, everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15531.0,
      "end_time": 16681.0,
      "text": "Sawubona."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20412.0,
      "end_time": 22618.0,
      "text": "In South Africa, where I come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22642.0,
      "end_time": 25197.0,
      "text": "\"sawubona\" is the Zulu word for \"hello.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26122.0,
      "end_time": 28844.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a beautiful and powerful intention behind the word"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28868.0,
      "end_time": 31980.0,
      "text": "because \"sawubona\" literally translated means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31122.0,
      "end_time": 34413.0,
      "text": "\"I see you, and by seeing you, I bring you into being.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35538.0,
      "end_time": 38458.0,
      "text": "So beautiful, imagine being greeted like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40930.0,
      "end_time": 43130.0,
      "text": "But what does it take in the way we see ourselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43370.0,
      "end_time": 45783.0,
      "text": "Our thoughts, our emotions and our stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45807.0,
      "end_time": 47139.0,
      "text": "that help us to thrive"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47163.0,
      "end_time": 50113.0,
      "text": "in an increasingly complex and fraught world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50958.0,
      "end_time": 54783.0,
      "text": "This crucial question has been at the center of my life&#39;s work."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54807.0,
      "end_time": 58117.0,
      "text": "Because how we deal with our inner world drives everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58593.0,
      "end_time": 61783.0,
      "text": "Every aspect of how we love, how we live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61807.0,
      "end_time": 63807.0,
      "text": "how we parent and how we lead."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64696.0,
      "end_time": 68481.0,
      "text": "The conventional view of emotions as good or bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68505.0,
      "end_time": 70172.0,
      "text": "positive or negative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70196.0,
      "end_time": 71346.0,
      "text": "is rigid."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71768.0,
      "end_time": 75510.0,
      "text": "And rigidity in the face of complexity is toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76930.0,
      "end_time": 79387.0,
      "text": "We need greater levels of emotional agility"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79411.0,
      "end_time": 81611.0,
      "text": "for true resilience and thriving."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83302.0,
      "end_time": 84985.0,
      "text": "My journey with this calling"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85900.0,
      "end_time": 88627.0,
      "text": "began not in the hallowed halls of a university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88651.0,
      "end_time": 90919.0,
      "text": "but in the messy, tender business of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91728.0,
      "end_time": 95363.0,
      "text": "I grew up in the white suburbs of apartheid South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95387.0,
      "end_time": 98910.0,
      "text": "a country and community committed to not seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98934.0,
      "end_time": 100840.0,
      "text": "To denial."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100578.0,
      "end_time": 105126.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s denial that makes 50 years of racist legislation possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105150.0,
      "end_time": 108522.0,
      "text": "while people convince themselves that they are doing nothing wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109461.0,
      "end_time": 113267.0,
      "text": "And yet, I first learned of the destructive power of denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113291.0,
      "end_time": 114624.0,
      "text": "at a personal level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115117.0,
      "end_time": 119132.0,
      "text": "before I understood what it was doing to the country of my birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121850.0,
      "end_time": 123649.0,
      "text": "My father died on a Friday."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124564.0,
      "end_time": 126764.0,
      "text": "He was 42 years old and I was 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127802.0,
      "end_time": 130635.0,
      "text": "My mother whispered to me to go and say goodbye to my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130657.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132209.0,
      "text": "before I went to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132234.0,
      "end_time": 135805.0,
      "text": "So I put my backpack down and walked the passage that ran through"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135829.0,
      "end_time": 138726.0,
      "text": "to where the heart of our home my father lay dying of cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139526.0,
      "end_time": 142316.0,
      "text": "His eyes were closed, but he knew I was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142997.0,
      "end_time": 145628.0,
      "text": "In his presence, I had always felt seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146331.0,
      "end_time": 147783.0,
      "text": "I told him I loved him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147807.0,
      "end_time": 150406.0,
      "text": "said goodbye and headed off for my day."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151984.0,
      "end_time": 156720.0,
      "text": "At school, I drifted from science to mathematics to history to biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156960.0,
      "end_time": 158292.0,
      "text": "as my father slipped from the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158889.0,
      "end_time": 161687.0,
      "text": "From May to July to September to November,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161711.0,
      "end_time": 163911.0,
      "text": "I went about with my usual smile."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164251.0,
      "end_time": 166184.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t drop a single grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166673.0,
      "end_time": 170339.0,
      "text": "When asked how I was doing, I would shrug and say, \"OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171292.0,
      "end_time": 173358.0,
      "text": "I was praised for being strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174108.0,
      "end_time": 176902.0,
      "text": "I was the master of being OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178673.0,
      "end_time": 180255.0,
      "text": "But back home, we struggled --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180279.0,
      "end_time": 183450.0,
      "text": "my father hadn&#39;t been able to keep his small business going"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183690.0,
      "end_time": 184227.0,
      "text": "during his illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184252.0,
      "end_time": 187283.0,
      "text": "And my mother, alone, was grieving the love of her life"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187307.0,
      "end_time": 188784.0,
      "text": "trying to raise three children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188808.0,
      "end_time": 190685.0,
      "text": "and the creditors were knocking."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191355.0,
      "end_time": 195190.0,
      "text": "We felt, as a family, financially and emotionally ravaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195553.0,
      "end_time": 199525.0,
      "text": "And I began to spiral down, isolated, fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200798.0,
      "end_time": 203916.0,
      "text": "I started to use food to numb my pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204733.0,
      "end_time": 206147.0,
      "text": "Binging and purging."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206893.0,
      "end_time": 210930.0,
      "text": "Refusing to accept the full weight of my grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211125.0,
      "end_time": 215363.0,
      "text": "No one knew, and in a culture that values relentless positivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 215387.0,
      "end_time": 217424.0,
      "text": "I thought that no one wanted to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219339.0,
      "end_time": 223606.0,
      "text": "But one person did not buy into my story of triumph over grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224751.0,
      "end_time": 228268.0,
      "text": "My eighth-grade English teacher fixed me with burning blue eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228292.0,
      "end_time": 230753.0,
      "text": "as she handed out blank notebooks."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231598.0,
      "end_time": 234131.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Write what you&#39;re feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235106.0,
      "end_time": 236256.0,
      "text": "Tell the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 236876.0,
      "end_time": 238876.0,
      "text": "Write like nobody&#39;s reading.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 240930.0,
      "end_time": 241307.0,
      "text": "And just like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241331.0,
      "end_time": 244952.0,
      "text": "I was invited to show up authentically to my grief and pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245395.0,
      "end_time": 247720.0,
      "text": "It was a simple act"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 247744.0,
      "end_time": 250354.0,
      "text": "but nothing short of a revolution for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 251400.0,
      "end_time": 255340.0,
      "text": "It was this revolution that started in this blank notebook"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 255365.0,
      "end_time": 257603.0,
      "text": "30 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 257628.0,
      "end_time": 259500.0,
      "text": "that shaped my life&#39;s work."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 260117.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263405.0,
      "text": "The secret, silent correspondence with myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 264656.0,
      "end_time": 265832.0,
      "text": "Like a gymnast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 265856.0,
      "end_time": 270387.0,
      "text": "I started to move beyond the rigidity of denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 270411.0,
      "end_time": 272515.0,
      "text": "into what I&#39;ve now come to call"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 272539.0,
      "end_time": 274700.0,
      "text": "emotional agility."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 278187.0,
      "end_time": 281409.0,
      "text": "Life&#39;s beauty is inseparable from its fragility."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283360.0,
      "end_time": 284969.0,
      "text": "We are young until we are not."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285807.0,
      "end_time": 287680.0,
      "text": "We walk down the streets sexy"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287704.0,
      "end_time": 290573.0,
      "text": "until one day we realize that we are unseen."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 293488.0,
      "end_time": 295709.0,
      "text": "We nag our children and one day realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295733.0,
      "end_time": 297990.0,
      "text": "that there is silence where that child once was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298140.0,
      "end_time": 299983.0,
      "text": "now making his or her way in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301900.0,
      "end_time": 305937.0,
      "text": "We are healthy until a diagnosis brings us to our knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307900.0,
      "end_time": 309351.0,
      "text": "The only certainty is uncertainty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309375.0,
      "end_time": 312977.0,
      "text": "and yet we are not navigating this frailty successfully or sustainably."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 314164.0,
      "end_time": 317171.0,
      "text": "The World Health Organization tells us that depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 317196.0,
      "end_time": 320805.0,
      "text": "is now the single leading cause of disability globally --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 321585.0,
      "end_time": 323385.0,
      "text": "outstripping cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 323410.0,
      "end_time": 325790.0,
      "text": "outstripping heart disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 326411.0,
      "end_time": 330505.0,
      "text": "And at a time of greater complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 330529.0,
      "end_time": 334770.0,
      "text": "unprecedented technological, political and economic change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 334895.0,
      "end_time": 336671.0,
      "text": "we are seeing how people&#39;s tendency"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 336696.0,
      "end_time": 340807.0,
      "text": "is more and more to lock down into rigid responses to their emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 342371.0,
      "end_time": 345438.0,
      "text": "On the one hand we might obsessively brood on our feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 346387.0,
      "end_time": 348220.0,
      "text": "Getting stuck inside our heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 348735.0,
      "end_time": 350204.0,
      "text": "Hooked on being right."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 351850.0,
      "end_time": 353212.0,
      "text": "Or victimized by our news feed."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 355124.0,
      "end_time": 357148.0,
      "text": "On the other, we might bottle our emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 357172.0,
      "end_time": 359156.0,
      "text": "pushing them aside"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 359180.0,
      "end_time": 362316.0,
      "text": "and permitting only those emotions deemed legitimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 364680.0,
      "end_time": 367238.0,
      "text": "In a survey I recently conducted with over 70,000 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367262.0,
      "end_time": 368996.0,
      "text": "I found that a third of us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 369704.0,
      "end_time": 370854.0,
      "text": "a third --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 371466.0,
      "end_time": 376366.0,
      "text": "either judge ourselves for having so-called \"bad emotions,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376390.0,
      "end_time": 378183.0,
      "text": "like sadness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 378208.0,
      "end_time": 380167.0,
      "text": "anger or even grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 382570.0,
      "end_time": 385804.0,
      "text": "Or actively try to push aside these feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387273.0,
      "end_time": 388923.0,
      "text": "We do this not only to ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 388947.0,
      "end_time": 391201.0,
      "text": "but also to people we love, like our children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 391225.0,
      "end_time": 395823.0,
      "text": "we may inadvertently shame them out of emotions seen as negative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 395847.0,
      "end_time": 397871.0,
      "text": "jump to a solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 397895.0,
      "end_time": 399375.0,
      "text": "and fail to help them"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 399399.0,
      "end_time": 402489.0,
      "text": "to see these emotions as inherently valuable."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 405300.0,
      "end_time": 410441.0,
      "text": "Normal, natural emotions are now seen as good or bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 412474.0,
      "end_time": 416662.0,
      "text": "And being positive has become a new form of moral correctness."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 419522.0,
      "end_time": 423393.0,
      "text": "People with cancer are automatically told to just stay positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 426434.0,
      "end_time": 429237.0,
      "text": "Women, to stop being so angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 431191.0,
      "end_time": 432590.0,
      "text": "And the list goes on."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 434000.0,
      "end_time": 435414.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tyranny."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 436303.0,
      "end_time": 438450.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tyranny of positivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 440752.0,
      "end_time": 442610.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s cruel."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 443210.0,
      "end_time": 444171.0,
      "text": "Unkind."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 446640.0,
      "text": "And ineffective."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 447728.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "And we do it to ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 450284.0,
      "end_time": 451817.0,
      "text": "and we do it to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 453373.0,
      "end_time": 456700.0,
      "text": "If there&#39;s one common feature"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 456940.0,
      "end_time": 459745.0,
      "text": "of brooding, bottling or false positivity, it&#39;s this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 460666.0,
      "end_time": 463790.0,
      "text": "they are all rigid responses."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 464586.0,
      "end_time": 466666.0,
      "text": "And if there&#39;s a single lesson we can learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 466690.0,
      "end_time": 469483.0,
      "text": "from the inevitable fall of apartheid"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 469507.0,
      "end_time": 472192.0,
      "text": "it is that rigid denial doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 473642.0,
      "end_time": 474992.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s unsustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 475967.0,
      "end_time": 478830.0,
      "text": "For individuals, for families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 478855.0,
      "end_time": 480500.0,
      "text": "for societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 480783.0,
      "end_time": 484863.0,
      "text": "And as we watch the ice caps melt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 484887.0,
      "end_time": 487593.0,
      "text": "it is unsustainable for our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 489831.0,
      "end_time": 491696.0,
      "text": "Research on emotional suppression shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 491720.0,
      "end_time": 494688.0,
      "text": "that when emotions are pushed aside or ignored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 494712.0,
      "end_time": 495912.0,
      "text": "they get stronger."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 496664.0,
      "end_time": 498878.0,
      "text": "Psychologists call this amplification."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 498902.0,
      "end_time": 502154.0,
      "text": "Like that delicious chocolate cake in the refrigerator --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 503610.0,
      "end_time": 504995.0,
      "text": "the more you try to ignore it ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 506124.0,
      "end_time": 509728.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 510744.0,
      "end_time": 512902.0,
      "text": "the greater its hold on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 514619.0,
      "end_time": 518191.0,
      "text": "You might think you&#39;re in control of unwanted emotions when you ignore them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 518215.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520857.00000000006,
      "text": "but in fact they control you."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 522126.0,
      "end_time": 524305.0,
      "text": "Internal pain always comes out."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 525680.0,
      "end_time": 526218.0,
      "text": "Always."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 526863.0,
      "end_time": 528395.0,
      "text": "And who pays the price?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 529244.0,
      "end_time": 530649.0,
      "text": "We do."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 530673.0,
      "end_time": 531823.0,
      "text": "Our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 532696.0,
      "end_time": 533846.0,
      "text": "our colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 535354.0,
      "end_time": 536504.0,
      "text": "our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 541354.0,
      "end_time": 542766.0,
      "text": "Now, don&#39;t get me wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 543203.0,
      "end_time": 544841.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not anti-happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 546213.0,
      "end_time": 547521.0,
      "text": "I like being happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 547546.0,
      "end_time": 549133.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a pretty happy person."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 550181.0,
      "end_time": 555958.0,
      "text": "But when we push aside normal emotions to embrace false positivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 555982.0,
      "end_time": 560982.0,
      "text": "we lose our capacity to develop skills to deal with the world as it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 562130.0,
      "end_time": 563696.0,
      "text": "not as we wish it to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 564950.0,
      "end_time": 568209.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had hundreds of people tell me what they don&#39;t want to feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 569180.0,
      "end_time": 570877.0,
      "text": "They say things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 570902.0,
      "end_time": 574440.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t want to try because I don&#39;t want to feel disappointed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 575220.0,
      "end_time": 578490.0,
      "text": "Or, \"I just want this feeling to go away.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 581235.0,
      "end_time": 583102.0,
      "text": "\"I understand,\" I say to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 584610.0,
      "end_time": 586261.0,
      "text": "\"But you have dead people&#39;s goals.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 587187.0,
      "end_time": 592537.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 592561.0,
      "end_time": 598854.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 598878.0,
      "end_time": 600918.0,
      "text": "Only dead people"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 600942.0,
      "end_time": 604577.0,
      "text": "never get unwanted or inconvenienced by their feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 604601.0,
      "end_time": 605910.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 605934.0,
      "end_time": 608230.0,
      "text": "Only dead people never get stressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 609101.0,
      "end_time": 610701.0,
      "text": "never get broken hearts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 611196.0,
      "end_time": 615140.0,
      "text": "never experience the disappointment that comes with failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 617195.0,
      "end_time": 620695.0,
      "text": "Tough emotions are part of our contract with life."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 621949.0,
      "end_time": 624274.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t get to have a meaningful career"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 624298.0,
      "end_time": 626930.0,
      "text": "or raise a family"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 626117.0,
      "end_time": 628895.0,
      "text": "or leave the world a better place"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 628919.0,
      "end_time": 631370.0,
      "text": "without stress and discomfort."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 632173.0,
      "end_time": 637530.0,
      "text": "Discomfort is the price of admission to a meaningful life."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 639561.0,
      "end_time": 642133.0,
      "text": "So, how do we begin to dismantle rigidity"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 642157.0,
      "end_time": 644157.0,
      "text": "and embrace emotional agility?"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 645791.0,
      "end_time": 647450.0,
      "text": "As that young schoolgirl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 647474.0,
      "end_time": 650841.0,
      "text": "when I leaned into those blank pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 650865.0,
      "end_time": 653254.0,
      "text": "I started to do away with feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 653278.0,
      "end_time": 656396.0,
      "text": "of what I should be experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 657254.0,
      "end_time": 660600.0,
      "text": "And instead started to open my heart to what I did feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 661103.0,
      "end_time": 662290.0,
      "text": "Pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 662679.0,
      "end_time": 663829.0,
      "text": "And grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 664838.0,
      "end_time": 666377.0,
      "text": "And loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 666401.0,
      "end_time": 667550.0,
      "text": "And regret."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 669972.0,
      "end_time": 672553.0,
      "text": "Research now shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 672577.0,
      "end_time": 675910.0,
      "text": "that the radical acceptance of all of our emotions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 675934.0,
      "end_time": 677593.0,
      "text": "even the messy, difficult ones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 677617.0,
      "end_time": 680363.0,
      "text": "is the cornerstone to resilience, thriving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 680388.0,
      "end_time": 683529.0,
      "text": "and true, authentic happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 685268.0,
      "end_time": 690205.0,
      "text": "But emotional agility is more that just an acceptance of emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 690229.0,
      "end_time": 692379.0,
      "text": "We also know that accuracy matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 693228.0,
      "end_time": 697751.0,
      "text": "In my own research, I found that words are essential."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 697775.0,
      "end_time": 700807.0,
      "text": "We often use quick and easy labels to describe our feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 700831.0,
      "end_time": 703466.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m stressed\" is the most common one I hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 703490.0,
      "end_time": 706871.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a world of difference between stress and disappointment"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 706895.0,
      "end_time": 710563.0,
      "text": "or stress and that knowing dread of \"I&#39;m in the wrong career.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 711804.0,
      "end_time": 713709.0,
      "text": "When we label our emotions accurately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 713733.0,
      "end_time": 717141.0,
      "text": "we are more able to discern the precise cause of our feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 717692.0,
      "end_time": 720680.0,
      "text": "And what scientists call the readiness potential in our brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 720704.0,
      "end_time": 723906.0,
      "text": "is activated, allowing us to take concrete steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 724513.0,
      "end_time": 727418.0,
      "text": "But not just any steps -- the right steps for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 727442.0,
      "end_time": 729442.0,
      "text": "Because our emotions are data."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 730109.0,
      "end_time": 734580.0,
      "text": "Our emotions contain flashing lights to things that we care about."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 734720.0,
      "end_time": 737791.0,
      "text": "We tend not to feel strong emotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 737815.0,
      "end_time": 741360.0,
      "text": "to stuff that doesn&#39;t mean anything in our worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 742251.0,
      "end_time": 744863.0,
      "text": "If you feel rage when you read the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 744887.0,
      "end_time": 749136.0,
      "text": "that rage is a signpost, perhaps, that you value equity and fairness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 749760.0,
      "end_time": 751736.0,
      "text": "and an opportunity to take active steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 751760.0,
      "end_time": 753966.0,
      "text": "to shape your life in that direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 755930.0,
      "end_time": 757276.0,
      "text": "When we are open to the difficult emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 757300.0,
      "end_time": 760736.0,
      "text": "we are able to generate responses that are values-aligned."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 761957.0,
      "end_time": 763942.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s an important caveat."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 763966.0,
      "end_time": 766386.0,
      "text": "Emotions are data, they are not directives."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 766752.0,
      "end_time": 769894.0,
      "text": "We can show up to and mine our emotions for their values"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 769918.0,
      "end_time": 771846.0,
      "text": "without needing to listen to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 772419.0,
      "end_time": 777712.0,
      "text": "Just like I can show up to my son in his frustration with his baby sister --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 778673.0,
      "end_time": 781239.0,
      "text": "but not endorse his idea that he gets to give her away"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 781263.0,
      "end_time": 783589.0,
      "text": "to the first stranger he sees in a shopping mall."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 783613.0,
      "end_time": 785141.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 785165.0,
      "end_time": 788195.0,
      "text": "We own our emotions, they don&#39;t own us."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 789520.0,
      "end_time": 793323.0,
      "text": "When we internalize the difference between how I feel in all my wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 793347.0,
      "end_time": 797260.0,
      "text": "and what I do in a values-aligned action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 797284.0,
      "end_time": 800475.0,
      "text": "we generate the pathway to our best selves"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 800499.0,
      "end_time": 801906.0,
      "text": "via our emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 804466.0,
      "end_time": 807199.0,
      "text": "So, what does this look like in practice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 808474.0,
      "end_time": 810292.0,
      "text": "When you feel a strong, tough emotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 810316.0,
      "end_time": 812291.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t race for the emotional exits."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 813203.0,
      "end_time": 816847.0,
      "text": "Learn its contours, show up to the journal of your hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 817625.0,
      "end_time": 819569.0,
      "text": "What is the emotion telling you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 821570.0,
      "end_time": 825371.0,
      "text": "And try not to say \"I am,\" as in, \"I&#39;m angry\" or \"I&#39;m sad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 825395.0,
      "end_time": 826554.0,
      "text": "When you say \"I am\""
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 826578.0,
      "end_time": 829125.0,
      "text": "it makes you sound as if you are the emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 829149.0,
      "end_time": 831878.0,
      "text": "Whereas you are you, and the emotion is a data source."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 832577.0,
      "end_time": 835220.0,
      "text": "Instead, try to notice the feeling for what it is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 835460.0,
      "end_time": 836734.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m noticing that I&#39;m feeling sad\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 836758.0,
      "end_time": 838780.0,
      "text": "or \"I&#39;m noticing that I&#39;m feeling angry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 840370.0,
      "end_time": 842155.0,
      "text": "These are essential skills for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 842179.0,
      "end_time": 844434.0,
      "text": "our families, our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 844458.0,
      "end_time": 846708.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re also critical to the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 848132.0,
      "end_time": 849300.0,
      "text": "In my research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 849324.0,
      "end_time": 852863.0,
      "text": "when I looked at what helps people to bring the best of themselves to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 852887.0,
      "end_time": 854560.0,
      "text": "I found a powerful key contributor:"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 854585.0,
      "end_time": 856519.0,
      "text": "individualized consideration."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 857840.0,
      "end_time": 860845.0,
      "text": "When people are allowed to feel their emotional truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 860870.0,
      "end_time": 864337.0,
      "text": "engagement, creativity and innovation flourish in the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 865661.0,
      "end_time": 867169.0,
      "text": "Diversity isn&#39;t just people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 867193.0,
      "end_time": 869534.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also what&#39;s inside people."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 869558.0,
      "end_time": 871625.0,
      "text": "Including diversity of emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 874425.0,
      "end_time": 878313.0,
      "text": "The most agile, resilient individuals, teams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 878337.0,
      "end_time": 880649.0,
      "text": "organizations, families, communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 880673.0,
      "end_time": 883421.0,
      "text": "are built on an openness to the normal human emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 884189.0,
      "end_time": 886497.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s this that allows us to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 886522.0,
      "end_time": 888600.0,
      "text": "\"What is my emotion telling me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 888624.0,
      "end_time": 891681.0,
      "text": "\"Which action will bring me towards my values?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 891705.0,
      "end_time": 894930.0,
      "text": "\"Which will take me away from my values?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 895436.0,
      "end_time": 899165.0,
      "text": "Emotional agility is the ability to be with your emotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 899189.0,
      "end_time": 902165.0,
      "text": "with curiosity, compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 902189.0,
      "end_time": 905954.0,
      "text": "and especially the courage to take values-connected steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 907891.0,
      "end_time": 909570.0,
      "text": "When I was little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 909810.0,
      "end_time": 911891.0,
      "text": "I would wake up at night terrified by the idea of death."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 911915.0,
      "end_time": 914947.0,
      "text": "My father would comfort me with soft pats and kisses."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 915677.0,
      "end_time": 917211.0,
      "text": "But he would never lie."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 918738.0,
      "end_time": 920856.0,
      "text": "\"We all die, Susie,\" he would say."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 921780.0,
      "end_time": 923625.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s normal to be scared.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 924483.0,
      "end_time": 928240.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t try to invent a buffer between me and reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 929370.0,
      "end_time": 930887.0,
      "text": "It took me a while to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 930911.0,
      "end_time": 933498.0,
      "text": "the power of how he guided me through those nights."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 934228.0,
      "end_time": 938361.0,
      "text": "What he showed me is that courage is not an absence of fear;"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 939579.0,
      "end_time": 942522.0,
      "text": "courage is fear walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 944791.0,
      "end_time": 947300.0,
      "text": "Neither of us knew that in 10 short years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 947540.0,
      "end_time": 948266.0,
      "text": "he would be gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 948950.0,
      "end_time": 951854.0,
      "text": "And that time for each of us is all too precious"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 951878.0,
      "end_time": 953780.0,
      "text": "and all too brief."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 954494.0,
      "end_time": 957287.0,
      "text": "But when our moment comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 957311.0,
      "end_time": 959509.0,
      "text": "to face our fragility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 959533.0,
      "end_time": 961232.0,
      "text": "in that ultimate time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 961256.0,
      "end_time": 962516.0,
      "text": "it will ask us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 963359.0,
      "end_time": 964659.0,
      "text": "\"Are you agile?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 965421.0,
      "end_time": 966571.0,
      "text": "\"Are you agile?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 967738.0,
      "end_time": 971182.0,
      "text": "Let the moment be an unreserved \"yes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 972381.0,
      "end_time": 976682.0,
      "text": "A \"yes\" born of a lifelong correspondence with your own heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 977784.0,
      "end_time": 979500.0,
      "text": "And in seeing yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 980839.0,
      "end_time": 983228.0,
      "text": "Because in seeing yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 983252.0,
      "end_time": 985718.0,
      "text": "you are also able to see others, too:"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 987218.0,
      "end_time": 990641.0,
      "text": "the only sustainable way forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 990665.0,
      "end_time": 993290.0,
      "text": "in a fragile, beautiful world."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 994972.0,
      "end_time": 996418.0,
      "text": "Sawubona."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 996442.0,
      "end_time": 997609.0,
      "text": "And thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 997633.0,
      "end_time": 998666.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 998690.0,
      "end_time": 999841.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 999865.0,
      "end_time": 1002135.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1002160.0,
      "end_time": 1003421.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1003440.0,
      "end_time": 1007416.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}